{"tid":2301694,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"用唔到BNO返香港，想問有無人最近係歐洲試過用BNO上機","createTime":"2020-11-26T13:19:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T12:52:17.000Z","uid":323420,"like":4,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"7db0543bede3c986a9b2c46fef9d11bc508a3037","tid":2301694,"uid":323420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T13:19:59.000Z","msg":"講少少背景先，因為歐洲一向都唔係好識分BNO同BC，<br />\n所以每次係歐洲返香港用BNO都會俾當地上機前check 證件嘅人問我有無香港visa先俾上機，<br />\n或者有時佢哋會叫我用第二本護照或我同佢哋解釋返BNO係香港有效入境證件／指返內頁個行&quot; The holder of this passport has hong kong permanent identity card no. XXXXXX. Which states that the holder has the right of abode in Hong Kong&quot; 就無問題。<br />\n<br />\n今次因為武肺要香港永久居民或者working visa 先可以上機，然後同一件事又再loop，職員話我唔係香港居民要我show ID card同要有特別字頭先可以入境，我又指左行字俾佢睇佢話BNO寫左我係香港永久居民我可以入境，佢再check 話香港 guideline 淨係寫左HKSAR passport / working visa / special permit可以入境，無寫到BNO。最後我講左勁耐個職員惱左話我再嘈佢有權取消我張機票。<br />\n<br />\n我返黎再問入境處，佢哋話無唔俾BNO入境。<br />\n平時都係煩，但今次好嚴，有無人最近有同樣經驗?"},{"pid":"3b7e6619de6d9d12b2bdd87f08c1ed203096857d","tid":2301694,"uid":167177,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T13:21:01.000Z","msg":"返黎做咩"},{"pid":"8c7a6798031adb22395632af0b636f44d1c2fa75","tid":2301694,"uid":230544,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T13:21:18.000Z","msg":"你無身分證？"},{"pid":"b85e02aa89f0a1568e8da651d0191a3b6090da25","tid":2301694,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T13:22:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bece0f1dd5d4e863f1c9fe8eee77390c6aa69596","tid":2301694,"uid":236422,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T13:23:21.000Z","msg":"通常都帶晒兩本passport 月頭返歐洲返 我身份證唔見埋都輕鬆上機"},{"pid":"c80c06ce5f7b1b0727f1cb83687ee4b107a4963e","tid":2301694,"uid":323420,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"8c7a6798031adb22395632af0b636f44d1c2fa75","tid":2301694,"uid":230544,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T13:21:18.000Z","msg":"你